comment:
* Exception type to be used for errors related to on-device intelligence system service with
 * appropriate error code.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_BAD_DATA
variables.comment: Request passed contains bad data for e.g. format.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_REQUEST_NOT_SAFE
variables.comment: Whole request was classified as not safe, and no response will be generated.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_COMPUTE_ERROR
variables.comment: Underlying processing encountered an error and failed to compute results.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_IPC_ERROR
variables.comment: Encountered an error while performing IPC

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_CANCELLED
variables.comment: Request was cancelled either by user signal or by the underlying implementation.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_NOT_AVAILABLE
variables.comment: Underlying processing in the remote implementation is not available.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_BUSY
variables.comment: The service is currently busy. Callers should retry with exponential backoff.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_SAFETY_ERROR
variables.comment: Something went wrong with safety classification service.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_REQUEST_TOO_LARGE
variables.comment: Request is too large to be processed.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_SUSPENDED
variables.comment: Inference suspended so that higher-priority inference can run.

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_INTERNAL
variables.comment:
* Underlying processing encountered an internal error, like a violated precondition
     * .

variables.name: PROCESSING_ERROR_SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE
variables.comment:
* The processing was not able to be passed on to the remote implementation, as the
     * service
     * was unavailable.

variables.name: ON_DEVICE_INTELLIGENCE_SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE
variables.comment: * Error code returned when the OnDeviceIntelligenceManager service is unavailable.

variables.name: PROCESSING_UPDATE_STATUS_CONNECTION_FAILED
variables.comment: * The connection to remote service failed and the processing state could not be updated.

methods.name: public int getErrorCode()
methods.comment: Returns the error code of the exception.

methods.name: public PersistableBundle getErrorParams()
methods.comment: Returns the error params of the exception.
